00:29:44,350 --> 00:29:46,550
And she's been
helping me do that.

784
00:29:46,552 --> 00:29:48,352
(chuckling)

785
00:29:48,354 --> 00:29:50,924
Thanks. I knew
you wouldn't understand.

786
00:29:50,923 --> 00:29:53,093
