(muffled talking)

787
00:29:53,092 --> 00:29:55,162
(continues
muffled talking)

788
00:29:55,961 --> 00:29:57,331
What?

789
00:29:57,329 --> 00:29:59,199
Amy had another drug dealer.

790
00:29:59,198 --> 00:30:00,358
Go on.
She used

791
00:30:00,366 --> 00:30:02,626
