before she got clean.

792
00:30:02,635 --> 00:30:04,635
But then Gillian
cut him off completely,

793
00:30:04,637 --> 00:30:06,367
and the guy,
he was super pissed.

794
00:30:06,372 --> 00:30:08,572
Right, and where can I
find this<i> other</i> dealer?

795
00:30:08,574 --> 00:30:09,714
I don't know.

796
00:30:09,708 --> 00:30:10,838
Oh...
No, I-I-I swear

797
00:30:10,843 --> 00:30:12,083
I've never met him.

798
00:30:12,077 --> 00:30:13,937
Look, he goes by the name of...

799
00:30:13,946 --> 00:30:15,306
of Bobby B.

800
00:30:16,348 --> 00:30:17,678
Lovely.

801
00:30:18,951 --> 00:30:20,621
I thought you said

802
00:30:20,619 --> 00:30:23,449
this case doesn't have anything
to do with your mom anymore.

803
00:30:23,455 --> 00:30:24,985
It doesn't.

804
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:27,190
Then why are you running off
to tell Chloe?

805
00:30:27,193 --> 00:30:30,663
Well, maybe there are things
you wouldn't understand
about me, either.

806
00:30:30,663 --> 00:30:32,203
(scoffs)

807
00:30:35,668 --> 00:30:39,268
So you guys are gonna
let me go now, right?

808
00:30:41,407 --> 00:30:42,767
Of course.

809
00:30:42,775 --> 00:30:43,805
(chuckles)

810
00:30:44,844 --> 00:30:47,284
After I've had my fun.

811
00:30:47,279 --> 00:30:49,109
(indistinct radio transmission)

812
00:30:49,114 --> 00:30:51,424
Ah, there you are!
Oh, hey.

813
00:30:51,417 --> 00:30:53,717
I've got some news
on the case.
Oh, me, too.

814
00:30:53,719 --> 00:30:55,569
But go on.
Ladies first.

815
00:30:55,570 --> 00:30:57,420
Well, our drug dealer's
alibi is still shaky.

816
00:30:57,423 --> 00:30:59,823
Uh, but he did mention
there's another dealer.

817
00:30:59,825 --> 00:31:02,485
Oh. That's what<i> I</i> had.
And Amy's lawyered up,

818
00:31:02,494 --> 00:31:04,434
so we can't get
anything out of her.

819
00:31:04,430 --> 00:31:06,300
And all we have on
this "other dealer"

820
00:31:06,298 --> 00:31:08,168
is that he's selling
prescription pills.

821
00:31:08,167 --> 00:31:09,397
Oxys. Percocet.

822
00:31:09,401 --> 00:31:11,971
Oh, not my faves, but
they'll do in a pinch.

823
00:31:11,971 --> 00:31:14,711
So if the story stands,
we're looking for someone
in health care: doctor,

824
00:31:14,707 --> 00:31:16,837
pharmacist.
I'm gonna go through
these booking sheets

825
00:31:16,842 --> 00:31:20,142
