987
00:38:22,668 --> 00:38:23,968
So how'd you put this together?

988
00:38:23,969 --> 00:38:26,039
Well, I was on
the Devil's business, Detective.

989
00:38:27,506 --> 00:38:29,236
(chuckles)
Look, even if I told you,

990
00:38:29,241 --> 00:38:30,941
