Filled in all the gaps.

996
00:38:42,788 --> 00:38:44,318
But?

997
00:38:44,323 --> 00:38:46,323
(sighs)
But I don't buy it.

998
00:38:47,292 --> 00:38:48,562
I don't accept
that you're crazy,

999
00:38:48,560 --> 00:38:50,960
