"Doc, you got to help me.

1005
00:39:00,138 --> 00:39:02,008
My brother's crazy.
He thinks he's a chicken."

1006
00:39:02,007 --> 00:39:03,967
(chuckles)
And the doc goes,
"Well, why don't

1007
00:39:03,975 --> 00:39:05,435
you turn him in?" The guy goes,

1008
00:39:05,444 --> 00:39:09,484
