1010
00:39:10,849 --> 00:39:11,849
Yeah.

1011
00:39:11,850 --> 00:39:13,580
(sighs)

1012
00:39:13,585 --> 00:39:16,045
Look,

1013
00:39:16,054 --> 00:39:18,464
